# ChronoAI's Grok (xAI) key — SERVER-SIDE ONLY.
#
# This key is used by the serverless proxy at api/chronoai.js, not by
# the browser, so it must NOT be prefixed with VITE_ (that prefix is
# what tells Vite to bundle a variable into client-side code).
#
# Local dev with `vercel dev`: copy this file to `.env` and fill in
# your real key — `vercel dev` reads plain env vars from `.env`.
#
# Production on Vercel: set this in Project Settings -> Environment
# Variables instead of committing a `.env` file.
#
# Get a key from https://console.groq.com/keys
GROQ_API_KEY=your_grok_api_key_here
